@startuml logical-architecture-its-detail
!include ../_shared/its-uml-style.puml

title Issue Tracking System - Logical Architecture Detail

top to bottom direction

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 28
skinparam ranksep 36
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam rectangle {
  FontSize 12
  BorderColor #37474F
  FontColor #263238
}

rectangle "Presentation Layer\n--\nJavaFX UI\n  IssueListView, IssueDetailView, AssignmentView\n  ProjectStatisticsSection, LoginView\n\nSwing UI\n  AccountManagementView, ProjectManagementView\n  ProjectStatisticsPanel, DeletedIssueBinView\n\nBoth UI toolkits reuse the same controllers/services." as PRES <<boundary>> #E3F2FD

rectangle "Application Layer\n--\nUse Case Controllers\n  IssueController\n    registerIssue(), searchIssues(), viewIssueDetail(), updateIssue()\n    addComment(), changePriority(), addDependency(), removeDependency()\n  AssignmentController\n    startAssignment(), assignIssue(), reassignIssue(), changeVerifier()\n  IssueStateController\n    changeStatus()\n  DeletedIssueController\n    deleteIssue(), restoreIssue(), viewDeletedIssues(), purgeDeletedIssue()\n  AccountController\n    createAccount(), renameAccount(), changeAccountRole(), deactivateAccount()\n  ProjectController\n    viewProjectAdminDetail(), createProject(), renameProject()\n    addProjectParticipant(), removeProjectParticipant()\n  StatisticsController\n    viewStatistics()\n\nApplication Policies / Services\n  PermissionPolicy\n    assertCan...()\n  AssignmentRecommendationService\n    recommendAssignmentCandidates()\n  AuthenticationService\n    login(), currentUser()" as APP <<control>> #FFF8E1

rectangle "Use Case / Policy Partitions\n--\nIssue Management\n  UC1, UC2, UC3, UC4, UC7, UC15, UC16\n\nAssignment / Recommendation\n  UC5 four branches + UC8\n  status-based candidates\n  ASSIGNMENT_CHANGED\n\nState Transition\n  UC6 scenarios\n  fixer/resolver set\n  R->C clears assignee/verifier\n  F->R dependency guard\n\nDeleted Issue Management\n  UC9 soft-delete, FIFO 30\n  NEW/CLOSED -> DELETED\n  restore keeps reporter/fixer/resolver\n\nStatistics\n  UC10 viewStatistics(period, filters)\n  filters.scope\n\nPermission\n  UC14 included by protected UCs" as PARTITIONS <<control>> #FFF3E0

rectangle "Domain Layer\n--\nIssue Aggregate\n  Issue, Comment, IssueHistory, IssueDependency\n\nIssue Role Relations\n  reporter, assignee, verifier, fixer, resolver\n\nIdentity / Project\n  User, Project\n\nRepository Interfaces\n  IssueRepository, UserRepository, ProjectRepository\n\nValue Types\n  Role\n    ADMIN, PL, DEV, TESTER\n  IssueStatus\n    NEW, ASSIGNED, FIXED, RESOLVED\n    CLOSED, REOPENED, DELETED\n  Priority\n    BLOCKER, CRITICAL, MAJOR, MINOR, TRIVIAL\n  ActionType\n    CREATED, TITLE_DESCRIPTION_UPDATED, PRIORITY_CHANGED\n    STATUS_CHANGED, ASSIGNMENT_CHANGED\n    DEPENDENCY_CHANGED, COMMENTED" as DOM <<domain>> #F1F8E9

rectangle "Technical Services\n--\nPersistence Implementations\n  JdbcIssueRepository, JdbcUserRepository, JdbcProjectRepository\n  DatabaseConnectionProvider\n\nSecurity Support\n  PasswordHasher, SessionStore" as TECH <<infrastructure>> #F3E5F5

PRES -down-> APP : user actions
APP -down-> PARTITIONS : use-case policy selection
PARTITIONS -down-> DOM : domain coordination / repository abstractions
TECH -up-> DOM : repository implementations / technical support
@enduml
